<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="prototype.css" />
  <title>欢迎页</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="badge">👋 新版本上线</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">用创意连接世界</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        一个简单、高效的活动创作平台，让每一个想法都能快速落地。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">立即体验</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">了解更多</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-decoration">
      <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
      <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
      <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features">
    <h2 class="section-title">核心能力</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">🎨</div>
        <h3>灵活设计</h3>
        <p>丰富的组件和模板，拖拽式搭建，所见即所得。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>快速发布</h3>
        <p>一键发布到多端，自动适配不同设备尺寸。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>数据洞察</h3>
        <p>实时数据看板，活动效果一目了然。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cta">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>准备好开始了吗？</h2>
      <p>加入我们，开启你的创作之旅。</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">免费使用</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2026 OneFlow. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
